      "cve": "CVE-2021-37185",
      "cwe": {
        "id": "CWE-672",
        "name": "Operation on a Resource after Expiration or Release"
      },
      "notes": [
        {
          "category": "summary",
          "text": "An unauthenticated attacker could cause a denial-of-service condition in a PLC when sending specially prepared packets over Port 102/TCP. A restart of the affected device is needed to restore normal operations.\u00a0CVE-2021-37185 has been assigned to this vulnerability. A CVSS v3 base score of 7.5 has been calculated; the CVSS vector string is (AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H).",
